{"tid":1985621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"惡劣！台女孫姿燕向星國人故意打噴嚏被控「騷擾他人」","createTime":"2020-04-23T09:17:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T13:26:14.000Z","uid":35070,"like":107,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"d041be7b078fd46443cb5a97849c412dfb09353e","tid":1985621,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T09:17:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-04-23/396023?fbclid=IwAR09qjDD-UK6tuPn-OHCfE07JE_uHD3ewn_OJ8IAGA4wBMtTN0xZAxWVR_8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-04-23%2F396023%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR09qjDD-UK6tuPn-OHCfE07JE_uHD3ewn_OJ8IAGA4wBMtTN0xZAxWVR_8&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6pLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=92f8f4fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-04-23/396023?fbclid=IwAR09qjDD-UK6tuPn-OHCfE07JE_uHD3ewn_OJ8IAGA4wBMtTN0xZAxWVR_8</a><br />\n<br />\n新加坡新冠肺炎疫情截至22日，突破1萬例大關，由於日前發生一宗台女向新加坡婦女故意打噴嚏的惡劣行為，因此該名台灣女子同日被新加坡檢方以「騷擾他人」罪名起訴，最高可被判處入獄6個月。<br />\n<br />\n根據新加坡《亞洲電視台》（Channel NewsAsia）報導，事源一名46歲的台灣女子孫姿燕（Sun Szu-Yen，音譯）12日下午4時，於新加坡烏節路商圈商場ION Orchard入口處，向一名新加坡婦女故意打噴嚏，並且大喊「閉嘴」。<br />\n<br />\n孫姿燕22日被法院以「騷擾他人」罪名起訴，一經定罪，最高可被判處入獄6個月，或最高5000新加坡元（約10.53萬元台幣）罰鍰，或兩者併罰。<br />\n<br />\n此前，孫姿燕曾於去年6月2日，從位於三樓的公寓扔下丟擲地球儀、塑膠椅子、吸塵器、玻璃瓶與鉛筆，被控「魯莽行為危害他人生命安全罪」，此罪最高可被判處6個月刑期，或最高2500新加坡元（約5.27萬元台幣）的罰款，可兩者併罰。"},{"pid":"b78947c2e1befca11bd8e4d8168944a5ee0c71cf","tid":1985621,"uid":48358,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T09:18:29.000Z","msg":"孫燕姿"},{"pid":"19dc231d1d8eae9fe9f28f566294f9a1a7c166f3","tid":1985621,"uid":45246,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T09:18:37.000Z","msg":"孫姿燕"},{"pid":"324a0939b16fcebc340ad61f3be851f761e41c71","tid":1985621,"uid":82331,"like":417,"dislike":1,"score":416,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T09:18:39.000Z","msg":"睇錯孫燕姿"},{"pid":"8032e93404120195b007a98f76c2943278577ff0","tid":1985621,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0